mbda_2(W))\\sqrt{\\varepsilon}} \\right)$ and $\\mathcal{O}\\left(\n\\frac{\\bar{\\sigma}^2}{m\\mu \\varepsilon} + \\frac{\\sqrt{L}\\bar{\\sigma}}{\\mu (1 -\n\\lambda_2(W))^{1/2}\\sqrt{\\varepsilon}} \\right)$ which reduce the impact on\nnetwork topology (no $C_W$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Dec 2022 11:27:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-13"}
